<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_282_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als Jr vns nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd gebetten habt / <expan>Crıſtoff<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Laymıng<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l4">von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu ſchreıben etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l5">Vnd vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen . haben wır <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> von <expan>layming<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l6"><expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan . vnd auch mıt Jmſelb als er ſeyd bey vns <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt . <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
