<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l9">rıchten . Auch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſelbs oft von Jm vnd <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_282_r1l10"><expan>geſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> beſchedıgt / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
